’Щ@bfccd3f2460badf7196a4d7e69d377bab72663756e62d185e4780d8e4579aa11ЪКTitle: title: cal
Path: Flags
Content:
``--year, -y``
: Display the year column.
``--quarter, -q``
: Display the quarter column.
``--month, -m``
: Display the month column.
``--as-table, -t``
: Output as a table.
``--full-year {int}``
: Display a year-long calendar for the specified year.
``--week-start {string}``
: Display the calendar with the specified day as the first day of the week.
``--month-names``
: Display the month names in a separate column.
