’Щ@76df6dc35864048292e8d2867a37119913672d023213564d4490c9fc9eca9fc2Ъ·Title: title: cal
Path: Examples
Content:
This month's calendar
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> cal


```
The calendar for all of 2012
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> cal --full-year 2012


```
This month's calendar with the week starting on Monday
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> cal --week-start mo


```
How many 'Friday the Thirteenths' occurred in 2015?
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> cal --as-table --full-year 2015 | where fr == 13 | length


```
